<section
  id="principles"
  class="section wrap"
  aria-labelledby="principles-heading"
>
  <h2 id="principles-heading" class="section-title">How I approach system design</h2>
  <ul class="principles-list">
    <li>Design for failure first, not happy path</li>
    <li>Optimize for operational clarity, not just correctness</li>
    <li>Prefer decoupling and contract boundaries over tight integrations</li>
    <li>Balance velocity vs. safety based on system criticality</li>
    <li>Treat observability as a first-class feature</li>
  </ul>
</section>

